      "content": "ok i'll stick to the dose. but its actually getting kind of scary now. my chest feels heavy like someone is sitting on it and my fingernails look a bit blueish. i'm still a bit dizzy too. is it possible my asthma is just getting worse because of the pollution in mumbai lately? i'd rather just try to sleep it off and see how i feel in the morning than deal with a hospital visit. it's probably just the air quality right?",
